#

Stuffed Bell Peppers with Lentils and Rice

$10.5
400 kcal

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-Protein

Tags:

VegetarianHigh-ProteinDinnerStuffed Peppers

Description

Colorful stuffed bell peppers filled with a hearty mix of lentils, rice, and spices, topped with melted cheese.

Ingredients

  • Bell Peppers: 4 large
  • Green Lentils: 1 cup
  • Brown Rice: 1 cup
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • Chili Powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Vegetable Broth: 2 cups
  • Cheddar Cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
